        'meta_title' => 'Mt. Hapunang Banoi and Binacayan: Rodriguez Two-Peak Day | Resort Guru PH',
        'meta_description' => 'A DIY two-peak climb plan for Mt. Hapunang Banoi and Mt. Binacayan in Rodriguez, Rizal. Limestone trails, rope sections, transport, and best months.',
