        'meta_description' => 'A DIY day-trip plan for the Cavinti Underground River and the kayak gorge above Pagsanjan Falls, Laguna. Cave swim, paddle route, transport, and best months.',
        'tags' => 'Cavinti, Pagsanjan, Laguna, Underground River, Cave Swim, Kayak',
