        'meta_title' => 'Mt. Lobo Trail, Batangas: Quiet Day Climb Plan | Resort Guru PH',
        'meta_description' => 'A DIY day-climb plan for Mt. Lobo in Lobo, Batangas. Forest trail, cogon summit, Malabrigo lighthouse pairing, transport from Manila, and best months.',
